&nbsp;
<h2> Infernal vortex genesis
The event occurred at 2:53 > when a violent explosion at the base of the eruptive mouth > projected in lava > air and pyroclastic material >. Immediately afterwards, the incandescent powders were sucked by turbulent motions > near the crater, generating in a few moments a vortex > which began to rotate clockwise >, reaching an estimated height between 200 and 300 meters >.
