&nbsp;
<h2>Lo&nbsp;scatto by the Teseo screpolato</h2>
The shot, of remarkable precision >, was made by the Teseo Screpolato>, a sculpture of Igor Mitoraj> located on the south-west side of the volcano >, near Piano Vetore>. Giannobile chose this post because the statue, which symbolizes the modern hero > marked but capable of elevation, acts as a "silent listener >" of the messages of the volcano.
